Description: Cross Academy has day and evening students, but the latter have a secret: they are vampires.
Title: VAMPIRE KNIGHT, VOL. 11
Author: Matsuri Hino

Description: Poor Naruto: he must cope with a ninja summit and a target on the back of his good friend, Sasuke.
Title: NARUTO, VOL. 49
Author: Masashi Kishimoto

Description: This series is about an incredibly positive young girl named Yotsuba. In this volume, she goes to the store with Dad and thinks about learning to fly.
Title: YOTSUBA AND &!, VOL. 9
Author: Kiyohiko Azuma

Description: Tsukune Aono’s new school is filled with vampires and werewolves. How is a human teenager to survive?
Title: ROSARIO + VAMPIRE: SEASON II, VOL. 3
Author: Akihisa Ikeda

Description: Ichigo Kurosaki sees dead people and must help usher them safely into the afterlife.
Title: THE BLEACH, VOL. 33
Author: Tite Kubo

Description: In this romantic comedy, Haruhi, a poor girl at a rich school, is forced to work – as a boy – for the school’s all-male club.
Title: OURAN HIGH SCHOOL HOST CLUB, VOL. 15
Author: Bisco Hatori

Description: Sebastian is a loyal butler who moves easily from dinner parties to the underworld. Is he too good to be true? Is he even human?
Title: BLACK BUTLER, VOL. 3
Author: Yana Toboso

Description: From the publisher: "Get ready to brush up on world history with these handsome and hysterical personifications of the Axis Powers as they meet, become friends and form one of the most powerful alliances the world has ever seen."
Title: HETALIA AXIS POWERS, VOL. 1
Author: Hidekaz Himaruya

Description: The origins and true nature of Pain, Naruto’s arch nemesis, are revealed.
Title: NARUTO, VOL. 48
Author: Masashi Kishimoto

Description: Isn’t being a kid hard enough? For this group, who are also part bird, nothing comes easy. An F.B.I. agent steps in to help, but the evil "erasers" lurk around the corner.
Title: MAXIMUM RIDE, VOL. 3
Author: James Patterson and NaRae Lee
Contributor: by James Patterson and NaRae Lee
